- Democratic Republic of the Congo: 0 cases in 2019 (compared with 0 for the same period in 2018), onset of paralysis of most recent case: 7 Oct 2018
- Nigeria: 0 case in 2019 (compared with 0 for the same period in 2018), onset of paralysis of most recent case: 5 Dec 2018
- Somalia: 0 case in 2019 (compared with 0 for the same period in 2018), onset of paralysis of most recent case: 7 Sep 2018
- Papua New Guinea: 0 case in 2019 (compared with 0 for the same period in 2018), onset of paralysis of most recent case: 18 Oct 2018
